   647	
   648	Author: Kern (Fable designer role). The blind EVAL build (Opus runner,
   649	EVAL-BUILD-SPEC) surfaced two freeze blockers; adjudicated in
   650	`registry/assessments/l3a-parse-recoverability.json` (the interpretive
   651	record) and amended here. Both records remain DRAFT; nothing frozen is
   652	touched; the corpora at commit b4a21fc are byte-untouched; no phrasing is
   653	edited or re-rolled outside the spec's own remedies.
   654	
   655	### 14.1 Finding 1 — l3a recoverability 0.7167 < 0.95: GENUINE FINDING
   656	
   657	- PREMISE: strict blind recovery 43/60 = 0.7167; shape+entity-only ceiling
   658	  52/60 = 0.8667 < 0.95 with rel-label matching ignored entirely; all 8
   659	  genuine shape failures fall in unique-maker (3/4 sampled), made-lookup
   660	  (4/4 sampled) and out-of-scope-rel (1 control) — zero shape misses in the
   661	  other 13 sampled families (28/28 sampled in-scope covered items
   662	  shape+entity-correct; the earlier revision's 27/27 was an off-by-one
   663	  against the committed artifact — corrected §14.8 item 10)
   664	  [MEASURED: data/nlb-phrasings-l3a/audit-recoverability.json sha256
   665	  d6365bd95e7d61a1cce7585bb446aa8f905b2b8eec08d0756a446e2e70a09bf5].
   666	- Adjudication: NOT a scorer artifact, NOT an authoring defect. English
   667	  unmarked wh-questions are number-neutral and, for agentive noun relations
   668	  (maker of), orientation-flexible; the grammar's unique-vs-lookup and
   669	  role-vs-flip distinctions on NON-functional relations are not injectively
   670	  recoverable from faithful natural phrasings. Functional relations
   671	  (mother/father) recover cleanly via world-knowledge defaults. The finding
   672	  is a MEASURED instrument-level partial-negative on NL-boundary
   673	  reachability; the irreducibility reading is designer interpretation with
   674	  stated bounds (one judge, agent authors, K=1, English) — see the
   675	  assessment record for the full epistemic-status statement.
   676	- Registered hazard the gate preempted: by the pinned S2 definition, a
   677	  faithful unmarked unique-maker phrasing fail-closed-parsed to `lookup`
   678	  answers a singleton list against scalar gold and scores as a DANGEROUS
   679	  wrong answer; 43 such items sit above the S2 kill trigger (18/600) — an
   680	  un-re-scoped run could have manufactured the fail-closed kill from
   681	  information the phrasings never carried.
   682	
