-        {"claim": "coverage disclosure (mandatory): kernel-expressibility coverage 0.3542 at rung molecules-v0, MEASURED by m0b on one incomplete kernel-v0 instance — NOT general coverage; the 50 sheets are DeepNSM test-split words, a favourable authoring surface, and no coverage-general authoring claim exists here", "tag": "MEASURED"},
-        {"claim": "nothing here amends g9: its frozen record, blinded_review_done gate, GATE-H human review path and single review stage stand exactly as frozen; this record neither sets g9's review gate nor appends to its log; proxy outputs are quarantined from any future human reviewer (ASM-0553)", "tag": "BINDING-NOTE"}
